            <a href="#" class="viewmore">
                View more
            </a>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h1>Auto Insurance</h1>
            <img src="/images/ban2.jpg" class="smallbanner"/>
            <summary>
                Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old.

            </summary>
            <a href="#" class="viewmore">
                View more
            </a>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h1>Liability Insurance</h1>
            <img src="/images/ban3.jpg" class="smallbanner"/>
